    <div class="main review-item" id="6327656">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6327656/" class="title-link">一千个人眼中有同一个尼采</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6327656"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/summerday7/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u58261995-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/summerday7/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">盛夏光年</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-14"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-14 22:50:01</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6327656_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一直以为哲学家的作品都是高不可攀的天书，只有庄子这种“顽皮”的神话故事可以让我等凡人窥探一二 结果，惊才艳艳的尼采也能在你身边侃侃而谈，关于现在、过去、未来、梦想、成长、自己…… 他像个沉默的老者，只说寥寥数语，却总能醍醐灌顶。  关于现在、过去、未来  如果我...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6327656/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6327656_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6327656_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6349201">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6349201/" class="title-link">人类面临的普适问题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6349201"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zuogy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1019831-33.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zuogy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">左思</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-24"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-24 10:45:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6349201_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
